          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-666B37L1-line-1" n="1">
              <hi rend="display-initial">Y<hi rend="small-caps">OU'VE</hi> undone <hi rend="italics">Horace</hi>────what shou'd hinder</hi>
            </l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B37L1-line-2" n="2">Thy muse from falling upon <hi rend="italics">Pindar</hi>?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B37L1-line-3" n="3">But, e'er you mount your fiery steed,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B37L1-line-4" n="4">Beward, O bard! how you proceed:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B37L1-line-5" n="5">For, shou'd you give him once the reins,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B37L1-line-6" n="6">High up in air, he'll turn your brains:</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B37L1-line-7" n="7">And, if you shou'd his fury check,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-666B37L1-line-8" n="8">'Tis ten to one, he breaks your neck.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
